ing: 1 (5 ounce) jar green olives, drained and chopped
des: "Everyone who like green olives will love this dip. It's so simple and easy to make. Best served with corn chips."
ins: In a medium bowl, mix together the cream cheese and ketchup, adding ketchup as needed to make the mixture a light pink color. Stir in olives. Cover, and chill for at least one hour before serving.
